      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/bitcoin-slips-in-december-as-investors-cash-in-on-record-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币的破纪录走势在 2024 年底遭遇挫折，导致其自 8 月以来首次月度下跌。]]></description>
